name: HORSE COIN
description: Horse Coin is inspired by the spirit of the upcoming Year of the Horse — a symbol of speed, fortune, and unstoppable momentum. In many cultures, the horse represents progress, victory, and freedom. With this energy, our mission is to ride into a future full of opportunity and power.
